            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed background subagent rows in the activity list freezing with a false early finish time — rows for `run_in_background` Agent tasks now keep running until the task actually completes
- Fixed the sidebar hourglass staying stuck when a background shell task was stopped via TaskStop
]]></description>
